<item>
            <title>[LU-10129] map-on-demand set to 32 doesn&apos;t work on OPA</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10129</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;With patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/29290/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/29290/&lt;/a&gt;, map-on-demand set to 32 doesn&apos;t work. map-on-demand needs to be set to 256 in order for large transfers to complete. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
