                            <comment id="217532" author="ashehata" created="Thu, 4 Jan 2018 21:35:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;These list of patches don&apos;t need to be ported to 2.10.x. They were instigated by:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
