&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;which should hide the initial problem of discontigous fragments.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="217107" author="pjones" created="Fri, 22 Dec 2017 12:41:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Landed for 2.11. Flagged for consideration for 2.10.x until Amir is back in the office and able to comment&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
