                            <comment id="211900" author="simmonsja" created="Wed, 25 Oct 2017 00:22:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;While are looking to fix this maybe its time to revist &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7650&quot; title=&quot;ko2iblnd map_on_demand can&amp;#39;t negotitate when page sizes are different between nodes.&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-7650&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-7650&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="211849" author="ashehata" created="Tue, 24 Oct 2017 18:49:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here is a summary of my investigation on map-on-demand, and a proposal for a change to resolve the issues around this. I&apos;d like feedback to see if I missed something:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://wiki.hpdd.intel.com/display/LNet/o2iblnd+map_on_demand&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://wiki.hpdd.intel.com/display/LNet/o2iblnd+map_on_demand&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="211704" author="ashehata" created="Mon, 23 Oct 2017 17:05:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;At the LND layer RDMA writes fail. So that could translate to RPC failures/bulk write failures, and other FS issues.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="211612" author="ofaaland" created="Fri, 20 Oct 2017 23:37:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We do have OPA fabrics, so I&apos;ve added the llnl and topllnl labels to this ticket based on the following comment in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10089&quot; title=&quot;kiblnd_fmr_pool_map() Failed to map mr 10/11 elements&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-10089&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-10089&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;One thing to note, if you&apos;re using OPA you should use map-on-demand set to 256. I&apos;m still analyzing this issue and hopefully will have a patch soon. This issue is tracked under &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10129&quot; title=&quot;map-on-demand set to 32 doesn&amp;#39;t work on OPA&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-10129&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-10129&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I haven&apos;t seen&#160;unexplained symptoms on our OPA-connected nodes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;What would I likely see?&#160; disconnects/reconnects?&#160; Failed BRW operations?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
